{"tid":497578,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大發信確認張翔為下任校長 周五與學生會面","createTime":"2017-12-13T02:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T07:09:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2117be88bbe4ab221d880f0ef2acae114c1d8071","tid":497578,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:19:21.000Z","msg":"香港大學教務長韋永庚向港大校友發信，指校長遴選委員會已推薦在內地出生的美籍華裔科學家張翔為下任校長人選，張翔將於周五上午與港大學生見面，校委會於同日下午即開會商討。韋永庚更在信中讚揚張翔是學術成就卓越的學者。張翔是本港罕有在內地出生及受教育的大學校長。<br />\n<br />\n54歲的張翔在南京出生，並於南京大學本科畢業，在美國取得博士學位，現為加州大學柏克萊分校Ernest S. Kuh講座教授。2012年起亦擔任南京大學校長人才工作顧問，與中國科研界有一定聯繫。早前有消息稱，張在交予委員會的建議書中建議港大應重視科研、面向中國，提到清華、北大科研出色是源於獲得中國政府大量資助，因此港大應主動與中國不同大學合作，並接觸中國教育部以獲中央資助，發展科研。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171213/57575005\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171213%2F57575005&d=DGK2LAqmCD1msRExv7znd4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=4aa2e855\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171213%2F57575005&h=e7305c58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171213/57575005</a>"},{"pid":"81a0cd95b063db0dc45e4b5b4b45de3e49cd55b6","tid":497578,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc8cd3bdf48052a9e19eb9fba4ba2e52e1b8618","tid":497578,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e88190144a16de8a098cd4406aecc86b9d3bbc","tid":497578,"uid":37584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 